{"tid":467883,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"河口湖御殿場返新宿問題","createTime":"2017-11-14T01:49:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-20T05:33:44.000Z","uid":89533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"45891e95af77716ca112dae272e80f670100ae9c","tid":467883,"uid":89533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T01:49:41.000Z","msg":"新宿去河口湖就搭<br />\n<a href=\"https://highway-buses.jp/chi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhighway-buses.jp%2Fchi%2F&d=nUiqQaqfiwN1mylpE5SRoJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=99c60dfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://highway-buses.jp/chi/</a><br />\n咁河口湖--&gt; 御殿場<br />\n同御殿場返新宿/東京站<br />\n點樣搭最方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98e801340fe2e78353e730d48076fb4dc769b242","tid":467883,"uid":96171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:02:08.000Z","msg":"河口湖--&gt; 御殿場: <a href=\"http://www.premiumoutlets.co.jp/cht/gotemba/access/bus/detail18.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.premiumoutlets.co.jp%2Fcht%2Fgotemba%2Faccess%2Fbus%2Fdetail18.html&d=nUiqQaqfiwN1mylpE5SRoJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=0efeb412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.premiumoutlets.co.jp/cht/gotemba/access/bus/detail18.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n御殿場返新宿/東京站: <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.odakyu-hakonehighway.co.jp/route/outlet.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.odakyu-hakonehighway.co.jp%2Froute%2Foutlet.html&d=nUiqQaqfiwN1mylpE5SRoJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=eca4b3da\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.odakyu-hakonehighway.co.jp/route/outlet.html</a>"},{"pid":"569ed0e00dc421fbf60b6ff0524e2bc9ef3bb457","tid":467883,"uid":60279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:04:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新宿去河口湖就搭<br />\n<a href=\"https://highway-buses.jp/chi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhighway-buses.jp%2Fchi%2F&d=nUiqQaqfiwN1mylpE5SRoJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=99c60dfc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://highway-buses.jp/chi/</a><br />\n咁河口湖--&gt; 御殿場<br />\n同御殿場返新宿/東京站<br />\n點樣搭最方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你幾時由新宿去河口湖?<br />\n<br />\n上次我平日去,  新宿第2班車去, 好似係7點4上車<br />\n塞車塞到仆街<br />\n去到本梄湖芝櫻會場 11:20左右<br />\n<br />\n回程由河口湖上車, 出名準時既日本巴士都遲足一班車<br />\n本身我上4點車, 佢4點先黎班3點8既車<br />\n番到新宿7點"},{"pid":"0a873ce839488d43764df846bd67fdda606155b9","tid":467883,"uid":89533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:24:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>新宿去河口湖就搭<br />\n<a href=\"https://highway-buses.jp/chi/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhighway-buses.jp%2Fchi%2F&d=nUiqQaqfiwN1mylpE5SRoJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=99c60dfc\" target=\"_blank\">https://highway-buses.jp/chi/</a><br />\n咁河口湖--&gt; 御殿場<br />\n同御殿場返新宿/東京站<br />\n點樣搭最方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你幾時由新宿去河口湖?<br />\n<br />\n上次我平日去,  新宿第2班車去, 好似係7點4上車<br />\n塞車塞到仆街<br />\n去到本梄湖芝櫻會場 11:20左右<br />\n<br />\n回程由河口湖上車, 出名準時既日本巴士都遲足一班車<br />\n本身我上4點車, 佢4點先黎班3點8既車<br />\n番到新宿7點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n星期六<br />\n打算9:25am班車<br />\n我都怕塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但搭火車睇景靚 <br />\n但好似幾複雜"},{"pid":"5cccb04111d1edcdea8ade4e2455e543687654e7","tid":467883,"uid":10008,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T02:34:20.000Z","msg":"御殿場係指去outlet? 有巴士去，但要上車前買飛同早d排隊。好多遊客搭兼好多行李。架巴士只係普通日本單層巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 攪到其他站當地人上落車好唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\noutlet 有高速巴士去新宿。但會有塞車風險（但我年頭搭有塞但準時到新宿）。你驚可以係outlet 搭到火車站再轉鐵路返新宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a0c34906406b1268b3237fa4ce664da878fbc60","tid":467883,"uid":89533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T03:11:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>御殿場係指去outlet? 有巴士去，但要上車前買飛同早d排隊。好多遊客搭兼好多行李。架巴士只係普通日本單層巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 攪到其他站當地人上落車好唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\noutlet 有高速巴士去新宿。但會有塞車風險（但我年頭搭有塞但準時到新宿）。你驚可以係outlet 搭到火車站再轉鐵路返新宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴士班次密<br />\n如果搭火車點搭最方便"},{"pid":"c6fdf1cf80a571937ec8e7f22aca9c109c70eeec","tid":467883,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T07:20:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>御殿場係指去outlet? 有巴士去，但要上車前買飛同早d排隊。好多遊客搭兼好多行李。架巴士只係普通日本單層巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 攪到其他站當地人上落車好唔方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\noutlet 有高速巴士去新宿。但會有塞車風險（但我年頭搭有塞但準時到新宿）。你驚可以係outlet 搭到火車站再轉鐵路返新宿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n巴士班次密<br />\n如果搭火車點搭最方便</blockquote><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.odakyu.jp/tc/romancecar/timetable/c.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.odakyu.jp%2Ftc%2Fromancecar%2Ftimetable%2Fc.html&d=nUiqQaqfiwN1mylpE5SRoJ4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=27fe2d84\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.odakyu.jp/tc/romancecar/timetable/c.html</a><br />\n御殿場-&gt;新宿<br />\n特急Asagiri<br />\nJR御殿場線 直通 小田急新宿"},{"pid":"8b1b3d7faf986e371781cbe487e06cd4dbc6d768","tid":467883,"uid":157247,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-14T21:46:52.000Z","msg":"新宿去河口湖架巴士早d book定<br />\n我當時on99朝早去到諗住買飛 佢話full晒最早要到夜晚6點先有得搭<br />\n最後要搭jr 又要轉車又耐仲要貴d"},{"pid":"e63655cc6a3e134afabebf5dbd077ebceabd0a24","tid":467883,"uid":7076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T05:38:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新宿去河口湖架巴士早d book定<br />\n我當時on99朝早去到諗住買飛 佢話full晒最早要到夜晚6點先有得搭<br />\n最後要搭jr 又要轉車又耐仲要貴d</blockquote><br />\n我上次去又係full咗不過係我河口湖返新宿，所以一定要一早book定<br />\n果次好彩有jr慢車，用咗唔知兩個定三個鐘先返到去新宿🙈"},{"pid":"715f3658702b33fb61cd0a6b121c0c6b69803e19","tid":467883,"uid":46469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T07:42:16.000Z","msg":"我上星期日新宿去御殿場果程塞到仆街<br />\n因為途中前面遇到交通意外<br />\n<br />\n之後夜晚返新宿果程足足搭咗差唔多3hrs<br />\n先到新宿！！！ 塞車塞到仆街！<br />\n<br />\n可能因為星期日個個都入返市區<br />\n<br />\n雖然搭鐵喪轉線好似好唔方便，<br />\n但巴士來回我搭咗5小時 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可能係我自己黑仔，但地面情況我地預計唔到 <br />\n所以...奉勸各位<br />\n為免塞車都係搭鐵好d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3ed38f67e6d7d1395ae708126da11ff4e941e2e","tid":467883,"uid":3900,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:09:05.000Z","msg":"我搭巴士賴過嘢<br />\n塞車塞到pk...<br />\n<br />\n一程過又啱時間有 NEX 41號<br />\n(星期六日, 14:19 開車)"},{"pid":"9fb936a736807b323f83e8f922d2ee5d161a0304","tid":467883,"uid":119737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T09:09:27.000Z","msg":"我聖誕節諗住去河口湖 本身諗住來回都搭巴士 但幾個巴打都話塞車 係咪最好搭鐵路？"},{"pid":"1294a8c3834b1f2ef4e9584a63815ca1723bed1a","tid":467883,"uid":117425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T02:26:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我聖誕節諗住去河口湖 本身諗住來回都搭巴士 但幾個巴打都話塞車 係咪最好搭鐵路？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我同你情況差唔多,而家淆淆地巴士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da6899c35d499dc95a97852f34fc8928317b2e69","tid":467883,"uid":60480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:57:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我聖誕節諗住去河口湖 本身諗住來回都搭巴士 但幾個巴打都話塞車 係咪最好搭鐵路？</blockquote><br />\n聖誕搭過10點幾班車冇塞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fb64520c8bea69f4ea9cfd7d1768e7d33584335","tid":467883,"uid":60480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T03:59:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我聖誕節諗住去河口湖 本身諗住來回都搭巴士 但幾個巴打都話塞車 係咪最好搭鐵路？</blockquote><br />\n聖誕搭過10點幾班車冇塞<img src=\"/